{"tid":2171364,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"驗車搵HKMI or 專做個個Brand 既改裝車房？","createTime":"2020-08-24T00:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T17:50:25.000Z","uid":19725,"like":8,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd42b428dae08433ab95530b973165c5174096d3","tid":2171364,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T00:45:21.000Z","msg":"HKMI / IPMC : $1300 + $500 督電腦<br />\n驗大約1 hours <br />\n未必有得上架 ， 要IPMC先有得上<br />\n<br />\n問左一個專做個個brand 既改裝車房 ~ $1000<br />\n驗大約30mins 連督電腦<br />\n<br />\n爬左連登好耐 有人話hkmi hea 都係睇下有無大撞<br />\n有時睇漏好多野 有巴打話ipmc會詳細d 有份報告<br />\n<br />\n我諗法係<br />\n專門車房就成日要改車底配件 改引擎 改音響<br />\n你無返一定程度既關於個架車既知識都幾難做到<br />\n大撞應該點都check到 <br />\n督個電腦可能都specific 個個brand<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩諗法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />獨立驗車公司<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專門車房"},{"pid":"ba3e0fd1a76864bec7082e957e8708bf76acca91","tid":2171364,"uid":259877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"如果出去驗，個人prefer MI 多過 IP"},{"pid":"6de203c54f677731bdfeede2b9972a30de072e1c","tid":2171364,"uid":137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T01:02:57.000Z","msg":"我就搵過ipmc驗部fit仔，我覺得算幾好心機又有報告睇，d小問題有無撞過補過油都有check到，起碼一定好過求其去唔熟車房驗先啦"},{"pid":"a11813c404979ac29f45488f5b650e1a72052370","tid":2171364,"uid":101289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"要驗ipmc hkmi都好記得自己約唔好俾車行幫你約"},{"pid":"5ae58f3771c564c44e0255267117f9d87cc28bb6","tid":2171364,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11813c404979ac29f45488f5b650e1a72052370","tid":2171364,"uid":101289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"要驗ipmc hkmi都好記得自己約唔好俾車行幫你約"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"Why?"},{"pid":"c34d1901d68a0effefb7d190ccb629b3a88f9193","tid":2171364,"uid":101289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ae58f3771c564c44e0255267117f9d87cc28bb6","tid":2171364,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11813c404979ac29f45488f5b650e1a72052370","tid":2171364,"uid":101289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"要驗ipmc hkmi都好記得自己約唔好俾車行幫你約"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"Why?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"人地約自己熟既師傅過黎有可能有嘢扮唔知<br />\n所以有好多車行都會話幫你約"},{"pid":"933671f47f88acbcf15afa5520274b8278bac387","tid":2171364,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c34d1901d68a0effefb7d190ccb629b3a88f9193","tid":2171364,"uid":101289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ae58f3771c564c44e0255267117f9d87cc28bb6","tid":2171364,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11813c404979ac29f45488f5b650e1a72052370","tid":2171364,"uid":101289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"要驗ipmc hkmi都好記得自己約唔好俾車行幫你約"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"Why?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"人地約自己熟既師傅過黎有可能有嘢扮唔知<br />\n所以有好多車行都會話幫你約"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"都係自己上網約安全！"},{"pid":"7b9eaa265fc80a68e44c84c6b22271b2014a80d2","tid":2171364,"uid":306957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"上星期賣部IS250, 有買家搵車房驗，收$500<br />\n淨係篤下電腦依機直說<br />\n試d 門制冷氣制有冇壞，行兩行爆高轉試kick down<br />\n心稔我都識check la<br />\n又冇驗油厚度, 如果我部車有撞過，一定多謝依d車房助攻<br />\n$500做依d太好賺，比我係車房都會聯同車行去做尻HKMI<br />\n<br />\n好多人屈尻HKMI 冇上架<br />\n其實佢係有墊高部車睇車底<br />\n只不過上架望得舒服d咁解<br />\n需要睇既野一樣睇得哂<br />\n<br />\n利伸<br />\n第一次搵HKMI驗bB, check到撞過+太尺響<br />\n第二次check IS250<br />\n第三次就係賣IS250, 買家要求check"},{"pid":"2c311bee839307d93a4013bc0f642e86b42b8df2","tid":2171364,"uid":17826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"約過4次hkmi，第二次開始仲有舊客-100優惠。<br />\n佢地起有份list跟住去驗，可以清楚啲邊part有問題。"},{"pid":"c930ebf1bad33203b485bafc87cdf098b8feac1a","tid":2171364,"uid":192480,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"頂 ，click 錯了，我是想選專門車房的<br />\n<br />\n常見問題，一定是專門車房熟啦。"},{"pid":"64da0ec8c29204fbcbdc220a72c5c8a4ebd30428","tid":2171364,"uid":256615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"HKMI 電腦睇嘅只係好皮毛嘅嘢 用淘寶買到嘅 OBD reader<br />\n如果買歐洲車 建議你揾返有相應牌子廠腦嘅車房"},{"pid":"bb6d044391f45fbf786ba24d5de0a20f0e9b0d1f","tid":2171364,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64da0ec8c29204fbcbdc220a72c5c8a4ebd30428","tid":2171364,"uid":256615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"HKMI 電腦睇嘅只係好皮毛嘅嘢 用淘寶買到嘅 OBD reader<br />\n如果買歐洲車 建議你揾返有相應牌子廠腦嘅車房"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"我都係擔心呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9755e059f0c9799aa474831d5ab672ba81445792","tid":2171364,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78fdaa7cd986abc1dffff31c84aeae76ad3e1596","tid":2171364,"uid":33322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁如果hkmi/ipmc邊間好啲？<br />\n定係張list一樣，只係睇師傅？"},{"pid":"f765d617ac2bfdf5c78d315f1142da2cf87b787d","tid":2171364,"uid":306957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78fdaa7cd986abc1dffff31c84aeae76ad3e1596","tid":2171364,"uid":33322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁如果hkmi/ipmc邊間好啲？<br />\n定係張list一樣，只係睇師傅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"差唔多   兩間都